    <div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > SEGA [2,646 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega">SEGA</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio [486 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sega/ryu-ga-gotoku-studio">Ryu Ga Gotoku Studio</a> have released a new trailer for <em><a title="Games > Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii [8 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii">Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii</a></em> that deep-dives into the game’s naval combat mechanics. <span id="more-940350"></span></p><p><em>Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [8,708 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [6,608 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [27,620 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [13,721 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [22,200 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3061810/Like_a_Dragon_Pirate_Yakuza_in_Hawaii/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/like-a-dragon-pirate-yakuza-in-hawaii/9p1303fcxw6x" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Microsoft Store</a> on February 21 worldwide.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Naval Combat Overview Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Like a Dragon: Pirate Yakuza in Hawaii | Naval Combat Overview Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1msFPkAjAG4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-